{"tid":644140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[強大了] 解放日報：有美國公司涉嫌侵犯中國芯片設備專利","createTime":"2018-04-27T04:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T10:17:24.000Z","uid":141151,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e92712b504ba7a0b772ca8e70bf2c452c88ed52e","tid":644140,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T04:36:35.000Z","msg":"【強國芯戰】解放日報：有美國公司涉嫌侵犯中國芯片設備專利<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180427/58124031\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180427%2F58124031&d=ZbLDp%2FSOqoVC0pFaSHQ%2Fr8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=0fb6bd68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180427%2F58124031&h=50d43d86\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180427/58124031</a><br />\n<br />\n內地《解放日報》旗下上觀報道，中微半導體設備與美國某公司發生知識産權糾紛。今年年初，中微公司獲悉，美方涉嫌侵犯中微公司專利權的設備即將從上海浦東國際機場進口，隨即向上海海關提出扣留侵權嫌疑貨物的申請。根據權利人申請，上海海關暫停涉嫌侵權設備的通關，這批設備貨值達3,400萬人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n隨着海關介入執法，美方開始正視中微公司的自主研發專利及其在中國的知識產權狀況，主動與中微公司展開談判，雙方最終達成全球範圍相互授權的和解協定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b046ace3c6836f62c17c4ac840be7409443b569d","tid":644140,"uid":62646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T04:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e701ec31c2bf6d50828274b126fddf6b94a23c4","tid":644140,"uid":38056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T04:42:08.000Z","msg":"又諗起new balance"},{"pid":"7fdc706ff3a10a8f6e6809b4e9c9df1bc733a81d","tid":644140,"uid":173741,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T04:43:25.000Z","msg":"再吹大啲啦<im